rows.label: tev015102_MSG0001
rows.name: I'm the older twin, Lara Nara.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0002
rows.name: I'm the younger twin, Lara Mara.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0003
rows.name:
And were are...the Beautiful Mediator Brothers!
...Well? Did you see that coming?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_SEL0011
rows.name: Claim that you had figured it out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0004
rows.name:
Nice work! And your reward is...a hug!
Come get some, [ST:gender p1=guy p2=girl ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0007
rows.name:
That's what I was hoping for! But I'm sorry if we
surprised you. Here, I'll make it up to you with a hug.
Come get some, [ST:gender p1=guy p2=girl ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0010
rows.name:
Come now! Save this fooling around for later!
...Anyway, as you can see, we're the best of friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0011
rows.name:
I promise that it was never our intent to deceive you.
I'm sorry if we caught you by surprise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0014
rows.name:
It's been so captivating watching you grow into such
a splendid [ST:gender p1=man! p2=woman! ] So what do you say?
Care to swing by our room at the barracks tonight?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0015
rows.name:
Stop doing that already! When you finally meet the
person of your dreams, you'll regret this behavior.
Don't take him seriously, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0016
rows.name:
That's easy for you to say, Naraâ€”you've met the man
of your dreams! You've forgotten what it's like to yearn
for the warmth of human contact...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0019
rows.name: It's been so much fun for us to watch you grow up![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0020
rows.name:
You're stronger now than any man in New LA.
I dub thee...the manliest BLADE of all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0021
rows.name: Nara! No woman wants to be called that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015102_MSG0022
rows.name: Really? I thought it sounded cool.[ST:wait ]
